# Below are aliases designed to be easy to use for
# people using voice dictation software.
# --------------------------------------------------------------
# These aliases differ from the more usual three letter acronyms because I'm using
# voice dictation software, so whole words are quicker and # easier than using TLAs. 
# This makes it easier for those with disabilities to interact with the Terminal using their voice.
# DragonDictate sometimes capitalises words in a rather erratic way, with no option to change that behaviour I've added aliases in both the lower and upper case.

